$interpreted: Nolva: ……….
Nolva: Eh? How did I suddenly get to Dr. Clovis' place? Have I fallen asleep again?
Kittyeyes: Yup. Thankfully it was only for a few hours this time.
Nolva: I'm sorry... has my "other" caused any trouble?
Kittyeyes: Not at all, he was a huge help.
Dagger: Is this the doctor's home you spoke of? What is he like?
Nolva: Doctor Clovis is a very passionate man.
Nolva: He poured his heart and soul into keeping my symptoms under control back in the old days.
Kittyeyes: He's got an ice box where his heart used to be. Completely coldblooded, not worth a mention!
Dagger: Both of you are describing... the same person?
Kittyeyes: Once bro is treated, we're leaving, stat!
Nolva: Dr. Clovis, sorry for disturbing you.
Aosta: Nolva Carpenter?
Aosta: Yet another Beast and two females come knocking...
Nolva: Doctor, Roger's void disease is acting up again. Would you please take a look?
Aosta: Didn't I once say you'll have to bring him to me?
Kittyeyes: You also said, the longer the experiment materials are active, the better effect they have on your research. Stop wasting time and treat Roger!
Aosta: Hmph. Lay him down.
Nolva: Dr. Clovis, what's happening to Roger?
Aosta: Just a matter of internal imbalance. Tame the Soul Energy and he'll be fine.
Aosta: These materials are required for me to treat Roger. Go and collect them for me.
Dagger: Red wolf fur...you need that much?
Aosta: Hmm, if this works out as I hope, Roger might be able to regain his old memories.
Kittyeyes: REALLY?! What am I waiting for? I'M OFF!
Nolva: Kittyeyes, don't go alone, wait...
Dagger: I have some responsibilities. I'm off to help as well, see you later.
Dagger: Where'd Kittyeyes scamper off to?
Dagger: !?
Kittyeyes: Huff...puff...just a few more...
Dagger: You defeated so many  of them in such little time...why are you working so hard?
Kittyeyes: If Roger can get back his old memories, then I...
Dagger: Get back his old memories?
Kittyeyes: Forget it. Let's bring these back.
